comment.pt:
Atividade econômica realizada pela empresa. Uma empresa possui uma atividade primária e pode possuir (opcionalmente) N atividades secundárias.
Esta atividade é representada pelo código Classificação Nacional de Atividades Econômicas (CNAE).
comment.en:
Economic activity carried out by the company. A company has a primary activity and can (optionally) have N secondary activities.
This activity is represented by the Classificação Nacional de Atividades Econômicas (CNAE) code.

comment.pt: Representa a versão da tabela de Classificação Nacional de Atividades Econômicas (CNAE ) à qual a atividade econômica está associada
comment.en: Represents the version of the Classificação Nacional de Atividades Econômicas (CNAE )  table to which economic activity is associated

definition.value: skos:broaderTransitive is a transitive superproperty of skos:broader.

scopeNote.value: By convention, skos:broaderTransitive is not used to make assertions. Rather, the properties can be used to draw inferences about the transitive closure of the hierarchical relation, which is useful e.g. when implementing a simple query expansion algorithm in a search application.

definition.value: A notation, also known as classification code, is a string of characters such as "T58.5" or "303.4833" used to uniquely identify a concept within the scope of a given concept scheme.

scopeNote.value: By convention, skos:notation is used with a typed literal in the object position of the triple.

definition.value: An alternative lexical label for a resource.

example.value: Acronyms, abbreviations, spelling variants, and irregular plural/singular forms may be included among the alternative labels for a concept. Mis-spelled terms are normally included as hidden labels (see skos:hiddenLabel).

comment.en: The range of skos:altLabel is the class of RDF plain literals.
